Simon Game

// Variables
rest - boolean
activeGame - boolean
userSequence - object
simonSequence - object
colorButtons - array
inputState - array
outputState - array
round - object


// Layout Elements
Create 3 buttons with equal class names & unique  (color)
Create round ticker / display
Create start button
Create strict mode button

// User Story 
User can start game by clicking a button
Game sends users a sequence of button patterns - buttons light up / make sound
Input button sequence (from index 0)
  If matches - recurse to step 2 + 1
  If mistake - stop, alert of error, reset option
If user makes it to round 10, then alert of win, and provide option for rest


// Facts
Go 10 rounds then game ends with a user win
